The inspiration for this recipe came from...the sauerkraut I make! Weird, right? But the flavors of the cabbage and jalapeño work so well together and adding turkey makes it into a complete meal! Feel free to swap chicken or other protein in place of the turkey.	





![cover1.jpg](/content/cover1.jpg)



<br>

	Ingredients:

* 1 T olive oil

* 1 clove garlic

* 1 cup chopped cabbage

* I jalapeño, chopped and seeds removed

* 4 cups chicken, water, or vegetable broth

* 1 cup cooked turkey (or chicken)

* 1 tsp cumin

* Salt & Pepper to taste

